Get_Transition_Array_Agilent_Compound_Test
Public Sub Get_Transition_Array_Agilent_Compound_Test()
Description

  • CompoundTableForm_Qualifier.csv

Function will assert if Transition_Name_And_Qualifier_Transition_Column_Indexes is {"1", "10", "14", "18"}.

Function will assert if Transition_Array has 15 elements

Function will assert if Transition_Array is able to get two qualifiers for Sph d16:1 and three qualifiers for Sph d18:0

First three elements are {"Sph d16:1", "Qualifier (272.2 -> 236.1)", "Qualifier (272.2 -> 224.1)"}

The sixth to ninth elements are {"Sph d18:0", "Qualifier (302.3 -> 266.2)", "Qualifier (302.3 -> 254.2)", "Qualifier (302.3 -> 60.2)"}
